{"data":[{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 13/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/2: Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938894\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938894\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</strong> HLV Antonio Conte m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 Alvaro Morata ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/2: Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-13-2-Morata-cai-loi-Conte-quyet-chi-tro-lai-gettyimages-852322698-1518461303-755-width660height495.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Morata kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Conte</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham nh\u1eadn hung tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Juventus. </strong>Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Toby Alderweireld ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Pochettino kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Alderweireld v\u00ec e ng\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Madrid m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Neymar.</strong> H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Marcelo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf \u0110T Brazil, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y c\u1eadu em Neymar s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 PSG, Marcelo cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Real Madid\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abramovich quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Batshuayi.</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Hans-Joachim Watzke, Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Chelsea, Michy Batshuayi. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Chelsea, Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham e s\u1ee3 Dybala.</strong> HLV Mauricio Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Paulo Dybala c\u1ee7a Juventus. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cDybala l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 cho Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi Tottenham \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Juventus\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU thua s\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n: Mourinho b\u00e1n g\u1ea5p 4 SAO\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-12/mu8-1518448724-77-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU thua s\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n: Mourinho b\u00e1n g\u1ea5p 4 SAO</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-13-2-morata-cai-loi-conte-quyet-chi-tro-lai-c409a938894.html","id":"376"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 12/02/2018 06:19 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 12/2: Man City s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938609\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938609\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Man City s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford: </strong>MU v\u1eeba thua Newcastle v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Man City kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu h\u1eb9p. Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f2n 11 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 Arsenal, Chelsea, Stoke, Brighton, Everton v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh MU. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, \"The Citizens\" s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng quang ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 12/2: Man City s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-12/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-12-2-Man-City-se-vo-dich-tai-Old-Trafford-hot-mc-1518391011-57-width660height404.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Man City c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho thay Pogba v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt:</strong> Pogba ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i 66 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u00f2 m\u00f2. C\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 trong l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1c b\u1ecf. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 55 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00fat Pogba kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Carrick ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00ec l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Van Dijk h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Southampton:</strong> Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Van Dijk c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n St Mary's. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 2-0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Southampton kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Morata s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea5u Barca: </strong>Chelsea \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Barca. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Conte, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Morata \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00eam nay g\u1eb7p West Brom nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Barca t\u1ea1i Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c:</strong> Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 22 c\u1ee7a Salah t\u1ea1i Premier League. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ch\u1ea1m 2 c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb. Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0 Robbie Fowler \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1994/95. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool v\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u201dTi\u1ec5n kh\u00e1ch\u201d v\u1ee5 De Gea, mua SAO Real 4000 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-11/640-1518367363-805-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u201dTi\u1ec5n kh\u00e1ch\u201d v\u1ee5 De Gea, mua SAO Real 4000 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n De Gea cho Real, nh\u01b0ng MU v\u1eabn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \"kh\u1ee7ng\" mua sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-12-2-man-city-se-vo-dich-tai-old-trafford-c409a938609.html","id":"375"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 11/02/2018 04:52 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 11/2: C\u1ef1u sao MU qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec ung th\u01b0","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938437\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938437\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>C\u1ef1u sao MU qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec ung th\u01b0.</strong> C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Liam Miller v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1eddi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 36 v\u00ec ung th\u01b0 tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ee5y. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Liam Miller kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2004 - 2006, ra s\u00e2n 9 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 11/2: C\u1ef1u sao MU qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec ung th\u01b0 - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-11/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-11-2-Cuu-sao-MU-qua-doi-vi-ung-thu-liam-miller-2006-1518292594-740-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">C\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU, Liam Miller qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec ung th\u01b0</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cMkhitaryan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m so v\u1edbi Sanchez\u201d.</strong> Theo b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Jamie Carragher, t\u00e2n binh Henrikh Mkhitaryan kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez. Trong tr\u1eadn derby B\u1eafc London v\u1eeba qua, \u201cMicky\u201d g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pique c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 Champions League.</strong> Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde, trung v\u1ec7 Gerrard Pique \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 Barca s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t Pique \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mahrez cam k\u1ebft thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.</strong> Riyad Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cho Leicester trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i 1-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n v\u1eeba qua, Mahrez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>David Moyes chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</strong> Ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a West Ham, David Sullivan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 HLV David Moyes \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU v\u1edbi West Ham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a. Nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i West Ham, Moyes gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho xi\u00eau l\u00f2ng, b\u00e1n De Gea 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-11/640mu-degea-1518291382-955-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho xi\u00eau l\u00f2ng, b\u00e1n De Gea 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo Don Balon, Real quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n De Gea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-11-2-cuu-sao-mu-qua-doi-vi-ung-thu-c409a938437.html","id":"374"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 11/02/2018 02:37 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho xi\u00eau l\u00f2ng, b\u00e1n De Gea 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938435\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938435\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Real Madrid mua De Gea 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u00f4i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 De Gea. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \"D\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0\" phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 3 cho Real Madrid. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd Don Balon cho hay, \"\u00f4ng tr\u00f9m\" 70 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 MU 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho xi\u00eau l\u00f2ng, b\u00e1n De Gea 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-11/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-99-trieu-bang-De-Gea-den-Real-mu-degea-1518291269-639-width660height413.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">De Gea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho quy\u1ebft l\u1ea5y Dybala</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Sanchez nh\u01b0ng HLV Mourinho ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfa l\u1ef1c. \u00d4ng c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \"nh\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1n\" \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. The Sun ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Paulo Dybala c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 86 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 MU \u0111\u00e3 mua Paul Pogba c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mata mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tu\u1ed5i</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Juan Mata ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng n\u1eb7ng l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi MU. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam 11 n\u0103m n\u1eefa. Anh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 khi \u0111\u00e3 40 tu\u1ed5i. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Mata l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i \u00e1o s\u1ed1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Man City gi\u00e0nh SAO 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo tin t\u1eeb Goal, Man City \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Fred v\u1edbi MU. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng Shakhtar Donetsk. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 MU v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3. HLV Guardiola \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ukraine 44,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Arsenal thua \u0111au Tottenham: Mkhitaryan \u201dth\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d, fan MU h\u1ea3 h\u00ea\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-10/2-10-2018-10-14-37-pm-1518277536-591-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Arsenal thua \u0111au Tottenham: Mkhitaryan \u201dth\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d, fan MU h\u1ea3 h\u00ea</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Fan MU... kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Mkhitaryan \"t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh\" trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-mourinho-xieu-long-ban-de-gea-99-trieu-bang-c409a938435.html","id":"373"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 10/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HOT s\u00e1ng 10/2: Arsenal tranh HLV Luis Enrique v\u1edbi Chelsea","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938237\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938237\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Arsenal tranh HLV Luis Enrique v\u1edbi Chelsea.</strong> Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi HLV Luis Enrique, h\u00f2ng thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Arsenal hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d, thay th\u1ebf HLV Arsene Wenger. Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Daily Mail cho hay, gi\u1edbi ch\u00f3p bu \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HOT s\u00e1ng 10/2: Arsenal tranh HLV Luis Enrique v\u1edbi Chelsea - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-10/Tin-bong-da-HOT-sang-10-2-Arsenal-tranh-HLV-Luis-Enrique-voi-Chelsea-wenger-luis_1503getty_750-1518198930-603-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Enrique s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Moura s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal.</strong> T\u00e2n binh Lucas Moura gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00f4ng 2018 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb PSG. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd xung tr\u1eadn \u1edf derby B\u1eafc London gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham, HLV Mauricio Pochettino x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Moura s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n, d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pep Guardiola khuy\u00ean Mahrez ra s\u00e2n ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i Man City. </strong>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Riyad Mahrez trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0111\u00f4ng 2018 v\u1eeba qua. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 tin Mahrez ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Leicester n\u1eefa. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Pep Guardiola c\u1ee7a Man City khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria, r\u1eb1ng Mahrez c\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HLV Klopp bao dung v\u1edbi Lallana.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adam Lallana c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t phi th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi George Marsh. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Liverpool v\u00e0 U23 Tottenham. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, HLV Jurgen Klopp cho bi\u1ebft, Lallana l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Southampton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d Wenger b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sanchez. </strong>Sau khi Alexis Sanchez gia nh\u1eadp MU, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile v\u1edbi HLV Arsene Wenger. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng nghi ng\u1edd l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Sanchez l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, b\u1edfi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Arsenal, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chelsea t\u00ednh th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Enrique: Ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p, Messi-Barca lo s\u1ee3?\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/640x480-1518085673-536-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chelsea t\u00ednh th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Enrique: Ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p, Messi-Barca lo s\u1ee3?</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Luis Enrique s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Barca.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-bong-da-hot-sang-10-2-arsenal-tranh-hlv-luis-enrique-voi-chelsea-c409a938237.html","id":"372"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 09/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/2: Evra c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-937931\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-937931\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Evra ra m\u1eaft West Ham</strong>. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Patrice Evra \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi CLB West Ham sau khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Evra v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV David Moyes \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Trong bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft, Evra kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cEvra c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Evra c\u1ee7a West Ham v\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi cho Patrice Evra l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho West Ham\u201d, Evra nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh \u1edf ng\u00f4i th\u1ee9 ba.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 9/2: Evra c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\"  src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-09/2-9-2018-12-39-12-am-660-1518112556-582-width660height432.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 432px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Evra tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o West Ham</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neymar &amp; Mbappe s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a nhau</strong>. Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n cho k\u00eanh th\u1ec3 thao RMC Sport c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xavi cho r\u1eb1ng sau khi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i, cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 xoay quanh Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf PSG. \u201cH\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a nhau cho QBV, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1ch ra kh\u1ecfi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf hai chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn\u201d, Xavi n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Salah l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u00ec sao th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea</strong>. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf Liverpool nh\u01b0ng Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y ra ngo\u00e0i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9\u201d, Salah n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mkhitaryan ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Arsenal</strong>. T\u1edd The Mirror cho bi\u1ebft trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Arsenal, t\u00e2n binh Henrikh Mkhitaryan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Arsenal l\u1ea1i l\u00e2m v\u00e0o c\u1ea3nh bi \u0111\u00e1t nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 cho Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette l\u00e0m quen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zaha s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cho Palace</strong>. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roy Hodgson cho bi\u1ebft m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Wilfried Zaha b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, nh\u01b0ng d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 bao l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng\u201d, Hodgson n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 8/2: \u201dConte gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp\u201d\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/sp22-chelsea-2-1518064657-480-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 8/2: \u201dConte gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp\u201d</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt HOT t\u1ed1i 8/2: Tr\u00f2 c\u0169 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 phong c\u00e1ch hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Conte.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-9-2-evra-cua-mu-da-khong-con-c409a937931.html","id":"371"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 08/02/2018 05:52 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/2: Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-2-Messi-tu-choi-luong-khung-o-Trung-Quoc-capture-1518032607-473-width660height478.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t <p><strong>\u0110\u1ea1i gia Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p 3, 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Barca, Messi v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m&nbsp;b\u1eadn t\u00e2m: </strong>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo, m\u1ed9t t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barcelona, <strong>Lionel Messi</strong> \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t CLB Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/2: Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-2-Messi-tu-choi-luong-khung-o-Trung-Quoc-lionel-messi-barcelona_1f3hjv68zrc3q1nbwqgc3kdo63-1518032607-780-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Messi l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Barca su\u1ed1t bao n\u0103m qua</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2017, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 500.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 3,4 l\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u201c\u0111\u1ea1i gia\u201d t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i Chinese Super League v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 anh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f4ng d\u00e2n nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter, <em>Messi </em>ng\u1ea5m ng\u1ea7m cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean c\u1eadu con trai th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Ciro. Hai c\u1eadu con trai tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a anh&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean l\u00e0 Thiago v\u00e0 Mateo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea ch\u1ecdn \u201ct\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi\u201d, th\u00e0nh Milan x\u00e2u x\u00e9 nhau v\u00ec Conte: </strong>Nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u00ec \u1ed1ng La Gazzetta dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f9ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Antonio Conte (Chelsea) \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb \u201cThe Blues\u201d sa th\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Italia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3n \u00f4ng h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00f9 v\u1eeba b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Luigi Di Biagio l\u00e0m HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Gian Piero Ventura khi \u201cAzzurri\u201d kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm c\u1ef1u HLV Barca \u2013 Luis Enrique trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Conte r\u1eddi \u201cgh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng\u201d \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Evra t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u MU:</strong> H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Patrice Evra \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi sau khi b\u1ecb Marseille ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau scandal tung ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 7.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2018. Evra s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 27 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft \u201cThe Hammers\u201d khi CLB n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Watford v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 27 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.&nbsp;\u0110\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 18/3, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp c\u00f9ng West Ham \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 MU t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 31 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n London.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/2: Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-2-Messi-tu-choi-luong-khung-o-Trung-Quoc-capture-1518032607-473-width660height478.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">C\u1ef1u sao MU Patrice Evra \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp West Ham</p><p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao Arsenal \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Oxford l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3: </strong>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Hector Bellerin tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc danh ti\u1ebfng Oxford l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Arsenal v\u00e0 Barcelona, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/2: Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-08/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-8-2-Messi-tu-choi-luong-khung-o-Trung-Quoc-bellerin-1518032607-662-width660height504.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 8/2: Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c - 4\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Bellerin b\u1ea3nh bao \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110H Oxford l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c sinh vi\u00ean</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Nguy c\u01a1 cao ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf Europa League:</strong>&nbsp;\u1ede B\u1eafc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, tuy\u1ebft \u0111ang r\u01a1i d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n \u1edf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ng\u1eadp tuy\u1ebft. Nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng xu\u1ed1ng m\u1ee9c -9 \u0111\u1ed9 C. V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/16 Europa League gi\u1eefa Ostersunds v\u00e0 Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 7/2: U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Kim Bong Gil\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-07/640parkhangseo-1517999492-344-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 7/2: U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Kim Bong Gil</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Kim Bong Gil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd c\u1ee7a U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-8-2-messi-tu-choi-luong-khung-o-trung-quoc-c409a937680.html","id":"370"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 07/02/2018 01:49 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 7/2: Real m\u1ea5t SAO b\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u PSG","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-07/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-7-2-Ronald-Koeman-chinh-thuc-dan-dat-dT-Ha-Lan-re3-1517941285-135-width660height371.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Real m\u1ea5t SAO b\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u PSG. </strong>T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Dani Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea9y th\u1ebb. L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (UEFA) ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ngo\u00e0i \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 1 tr\u1eadn (v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng), Carvajal c\u00f2n b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 th\u00eam 1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Champions League. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, UEFA cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u01a1n kh\u00e1ng \u00e1n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Carvajal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League v\u1edbi PSG.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 7/2: Real m\u1ea5t SAO b\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5u PSG - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-07/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-7-2-Ronald-Koeman-chinh-thuc-dan-dat-dT-Ha-Lan-re3-1517941285-135-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Carvajal</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Koeman ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T H\u00e0 Lan.&nbsp;</strong>Tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0 Lan (KNVB) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ronald Koeman. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i, cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Watford nguy c\u01a1 treo gi\u00f2 b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn.</strong> FA quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra nh\u1eb1m v\u00e0o Troy Deeney, sau khi anh n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Watford \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea t\u1ed1i 6/2. Sau khi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ed1 9 gi\u01a1 ng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed9i, Deeney c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Courtois \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Conte</strong>. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy. \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn tin v\u00e0o Antonio Conte, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Chelsea c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 qu\u00ean \u0111i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra\", Thibaut Courtois chia s\u1ebb.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>West Ham tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, Moyes v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. </strong>C\u1ef1u HLV MU v\u1eeba gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n gi\u1eefa BXH v\u00e0 h\u01a1n nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng ba \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Telegraph cho bi\u1ebft, David Moyes v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \"The Hammers\" tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. L\u00fd do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a West Ham.</p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-7-2-real-mat-sao-bu-dau-psg-c409a937426.html","id":"369"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 06/02/2018 00:31 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 6/2: V\u1edbi Sanchez, MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Cup C1","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-06/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-6-2-Voi-Sanchez-MU-co-the-vao-chung-ket-Cup-C1-sanchez-1517851828-332-width660height371.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t <p><strong>V\u1edbi Sanchez, MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Cup C1: </strong>MU \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez \u1edf th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u0169ng v\u1eeba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield. Thu h\u1eb9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Man City xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Cup C1. Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lou Macari cho r\u1eb1ng Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef k\u00ed tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a MU v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft Cup C1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 6/2: V\u1edbi Sanchez, MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Cup C1 - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-06/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-6-2-Voi-Sanchez-MU-co-the-vao-chung-ket-Cup-C1-sanchez-1517851828-332-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Sanchez h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng m\u1edbi cho MU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a UEFA (L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u), Sanchez m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Europa League cho Arsenal trong khi MU \u0111\u00e1 Champions League, v\u00ec th\u1ebf anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Champions League cho \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng: </strong>\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. Eden c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Fabregas n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neymar \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca:</strong> \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Neymar c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ed1 c\u1eadu ta, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 minh b\u1ea1ch. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i n\u00f3i 't\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i' gi\u1ed1ng Fabregas, Pedro, Sanchez, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. Th\u1ebf m\u00e0 c\u1eadu ta ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2 m\u00e8o v\u1eddn chu\u1ed9t v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 c\u1eadu ta ph\u00ed trung th\u00e0nh\u201d, ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jordi Mestre t\u1ed1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aubameyang \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u sang Arsenal, s\u1ebfp Dortmund k\u1ec3 t\u1ed9i:</strong> \"C\u1eadu ta (Aubameyang) \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn. Sau n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n n\u00e0o v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. C\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n h\u1ea1i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3\", Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Watzke t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Leicester kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eadn Mahrez:</strong> Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Leicester City, Marc Albrighton \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi cho r\u1eb1ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111ang th\u1ed5i ph\u1ed3ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Riyad Mahrez. Theo Albrighton, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o t\u1ecf ra gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u1edbi Mahrez v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111i qu\u00e1 xa. Chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00f2i sang Chelsea th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u0103n SAO Inter, nh\u1eafm Vidal \u201c\u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p\u201d Pogba\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-05/mu2-1517849702-140-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u0103n SAO Inter, nh\u1eafm Vidal \u201c\u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p\u201d Pogba</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Perisic v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua th\u00eam Vidal.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-6-2-voi-sanchez-mu-co-the-vao-chung-ket-cup-c1-c409a937143.html","id":"368"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 05/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/2: Pogba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-05/23423-660-1517768406-762-width660height495.jpg","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Mourinho kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee5c h\u1eb7c v\u1edbi Pogba</strong>. Sau khi Pogba b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tottenham v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield, Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Pogba kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u201cT\u00f4i thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec ph\u1ea1t ai c\u1ea3. Paul l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb 1 tr\u1eadn c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadn th\u1ebf\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/2: Pogba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\"  src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-05/23423-660-1517768406-762-width660height495.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 495px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Mourinho thay ra Pogba \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua Tottenham</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zidane gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c thay ra Ronaldo</strong>. Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Levante, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn 2-1 sau ph\u00fat 81 nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2-2 \u1edf ph\u00fat 89 khi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. Zidane cho bi\u1ebft ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay Ronaldo t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f3 v\u1eady th\u00f4i\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Neymar l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1ea1m ph\u00e1t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong>. Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Barcelona Jordi Mestre cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu Neymar th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho Barca bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh sang PSG, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 PSG s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 220 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00f3 Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee1 ph\u1ea3i mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao. \u201cN\u1ebfu Neymar th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 di\u1ec5n ra \u00eam th\u1ea5m, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt\u201d, Mestre n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Drinkwater mu\u1ed1n xin \u00e1o Messi</strong>. Chelsea s\u1eafp g\u1eb7p Barcelona \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 Danny Drinkwater cho bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi xin \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Messi. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Messi, do \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m x\u00fac s\u1ebd ra sao khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u anh \u1ea5y l\u1ea7n hai. T\u00f4i d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd xin \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Leo\u201d, Drinkwater n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ng\u00e0y ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh ung th\u01b0</strong>. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho phong tr\u00e0o ch\u1ed1ng ung th\u01b0 to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u khi \u0111eo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00f2ng c\u1ed5 tay Unity Band. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p m\u00ecnh \u0111eo v\u00f2ng c\u1ed5 tay l\u00ean Instagram k\u00e8m theo d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng mua v\u00f2ng tay \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 4/2: Mourinho ch\u00e1n ng\u00e1n v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf Old Trafford\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-04/ne1-1517738120-164-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 4/2: Mourinho ch\u00e1n ng\u00e1n v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf Old Trafford</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt HOT t\u1ed1i 4/2: Mourinho ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf Old Trafford.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-5-2-pogba-du-bi-la-chuyen-binh-thuong-c409a936887.html","id":"367"}]}